This paper is about image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a method for multi-feature fusion ranking, which involves machine learning techniques such as graph structure analysis and manifold learning. Therefore, it is likely to also belong to sub-categories such as information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
